title: Everything You Need to Know About the Fast-Mimicking Diet
description:
Jillian takes on the latest diet trends and revisits some old ones. From the fast-mimicking diet and time restricted eating, to HGH shots and the CICO diet - this show is EVERYTHING you need to know to stay healthy and get the best results.
